00:03:08.670 --> 00:03:11.820
And it basically kind
of opened my eyes

00:03:11.820 --> 00:03:14.550
to food rescue as a
concept, and to the fact

00:03:14.550 --> 00:03:16.880
that food can be
donated, and that there's

00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:19.590
so much excess food.

00:03:19.590 --> 00:03:22.920
So we were basically--

00:03:22.920 --> 00:03:25.950
a bunch of us, a couple
of friends and I,

00:03:25.950 --> 00:03:29.190
were kind of executive
board members

00:03:29.190 --> 00:03:31.830
of that club and kind of
expanded it throughout the four

00:03:31.830 --> 00:03:35.940
