under our leadership,

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:44.320
were able to grow it out to
all the different dining halls,

00:03:44.320 --> 00:03:46.560
and basically grow it out.

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:49.127
And that kind of opened
my eyes to the fact

00:03:49.127 --> 00:03:50.460
that it's not just dining halls.

00:03:50.460 --> 00:03:52.860
It's also restaurants and
different food businesses

00:03:52.860 --> 00:03:56.250
that can donate their food, and
that there's such a huge need

00:03:56.250 --> 00:03:58.240
at homeless shelters.

00:03:58.240 --> 00:04:02.130
And so that first
experience paved the way

00:04:02.130 --> 00:04:07.980
for the first inkling of an idea
of RLC at Two Birds One Stone.

00:04:07.980 --> 00:04:11.400
We kind of did everything
on a Google spreadsheet,

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:13.650
