00:32:09.450 --> 00:32:11.910
So we were able to
do this because we

00:32:11.910 --> 00:32:15.180
have the kind of model
that we can continue

00:32:15.180 --> 00:32:18.450
to be able to be sustainable.

00:32:18.450 --> 00:32:23.010
