00:34:13.090 --> 00:34:16.469
But in terms of
what RLC is doing

00:34:16.469 --> 00:34:20.909
to help with the food insecurity
issue, as I mentioned,

00:34:20.909 --> 00:34:22.949
food insecurity, and
poverty in general,

00:34:22.949 --> 00:34:24.300
is a really complex issue.

00:34:24.300 --> 00:34:27.929
And nutrition is just
one piece of the problem.

00:34:27.929 --> 00:34:29.760
And food waste is going
to help contribute

00:34:29.760 --> 00:34:32.500
to the overall solution
to that problem.

00:34:32.500 --> 00:34:36.150
And the way we see it
is the amount of money

00:34:36.150 --> 00:34:39.159
that we can save the homeless
shelters from buying food,

00:34:39.159 --> 00:34:42.270
they can use that money to have
much more long-term solutions

00:34:42.270 --> 00:34:44.760
like job skills
training, shelter,

00:34:44.760 --> 00:34:47.110
